369c6aab57499cd60c23e61446a2584a5767","tid":811584,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:24:19.000Z","msg":"禁止通姦<br />\n犯法一方無得瓜分伴侶任何財產及子女撫養權，兼且要同第三者對受害人賠償"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:56:12.000Z","msg":"啲富豪點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf871551608a7e1ece0c15ebdc8aa081379e94f5","tid":811584,"uid":35696,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:01:26.000Z","msg":"簷篷擔遮<br />\n<br />\n公眾地方開speaker 睇片傾電話<br />\n<br />\n火車地鐵排隊企中間比人出嗰行<br />\n<br />\n支那蝗入境 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b69903462992ccbd408003b377f7315f18b78ad","tid":811584,"uid":194785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:10:03.000Z","msg":"歧視毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒撚需要人權"},{"pid":"1c6048e9e9ebf793f99f0fa4e70696889138743e","tid":811584,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81afef96840ce594ec9a4ad45635f406dec24ff1","tid":811584,"uid":29070,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:47:36.000Z","msg":"每人150人來港<br />\n所有行街紙嘅蝻要遞解出境"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"回少咗<br />\n呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}